## 2. SCENE TYPE SELECTOR UI

In the RIGHT PANEL "Prompt" tab, above the textarea, add a horizontal 
type selector row. Five icon buttons, one per type. Active type is 
highlighted in accent red. Hovering shows a tooltip with the type name.

Icons (use lucide-react):
  svg    → PenLine
  lottie → Layers
  motion → Zap
  d3     → BarChart2
  three  → Box

When type changes on an existing scene, show a confirm dialog:
  "Changing scene type will clear the current content. Continue?"
If confirmed, clear svgContent / sceneCode and set new type. Regenerate 
thumbnail as blank.

