## 3. ZUSTAND STATE CHANGES

Extend Scene interface:

```ts
interface Scene {
  // ... existing fields ...
  type: 'svg' | 'lottie' | 'motion' | 'd3' | 'three'
  
  // For svg: existing svgContent field
  svgContent: string
  
  // For motion/d3/three: generated JS code as a string
  sceneCode: string
  
  // For lottie: JSON animation data or remote URL
  lottieSource: string | null  // URL to .json or inline JSON string
  lottieUploadedFile: string | null  // /uploads/filename.json
  
  // For d3: the data payload Claude uses
  d3Data: any | null
  
  // For three: optional extra assets
  threeAssets: string[]
}
```

