## 8. SCENE HTML REGENERATION

The function writeSceneHTML(scene) should branch on type:

```ts
function writeSceneHTML(scene: Scene, style: GlobalStyle): string {
  switch (scene.type) {
    case 'svg':    return renderSVGTemplate(scene, style);
    case 'motion': return renderMotionTemplate(scene, style);
    case 'd3':     return renderD3Template(scene, style);
    case 'three':  return renderThreeTemplate(scene, style);
    case 'lottie': return renderLottieTemplate(scene, style);
  }
}
```

Write to /public/scenes/{id}.html atomically (write temp → rename).
Trigger iframe reload after write.

---

## 9. THUMBNAIL GENERATION PER TYPE

- SVG: existing html2canvas after 500ms — unchanged
- Motion: html2canvas after 800ms (wait for entrance animations to 
  partially complete)
- D3: html2canvas after 1200ms (wait for chart transitions)
- Three.js: html2canvas on the canvas element after 1500ms
- Lottie: use lottie-web to seek to frame 30 in a hidden div, 
  then html2canvas

---

