## 11. EXPORT / WVC — NO CHANGES NEEDED

WebVideoCreator loads /public/scenes/{id}.html via URL regardless of type.
All five types render in headless Chrome exactly the same way.
No changes to render-server/renderer.js or stitcher.js.

The only thing to verify: CDN URLs in scene HTML templates must be 
accessible from the render server's network. If deploying on a 
restricted network, swap CDN URLs for locally-served copies in /public/libs/.

